            "title": "上實從粵豐私有化獲23.29億元 料錄虧損5683.51萬元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上海實業(00363)公布，持有19.47%股份的粵豐(01381)私有化計畫已通過，上實藉此出售所持粵豐將獲23.29億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司估計，出售將錄得虧損約5683.51萬元，即出售總代價與截至今年3月底時出售股份賬面值的差額。套現所得在扣除稅項及相關開支後，淨額擬用作任何潛在投資、一般營運資金或償還銀行貸款。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14950133-%e4%b8%8a%e5%af%a6%e5%be%9e%e7%b2%b5%e8%b1%90%e7%a7%81%e6%9c%89%e5%8c%96%e7%8d%b223-29%e5%84%84%e5%85%83-%e6%96%99%e9%8c%84%e8%99%a7%e6%90%8d5683-51%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/00363.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-22 17:35:29",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "人行明將進行5000億元人幣MLF操作 期限為1年",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">人民銀行公布，將於明日以固定數量、利率招標、多重價位得標方式進行5000億元人民幣MLF(中期借貸便利)操作，期限為1年期。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14950123-%e4%ba%ba%e8%a1%8c%e6%98%8e%e5%b0%87%e9%80%b2%e8%a1%8c5000%e5%84%84%e5%85%83%e4%ba%ba%e5%b9%a3mlf%e6%93%8d%e4%bd%9c-%e6%9c%9f%e9%99%90%e7%82%ba1%e5%b9%b4",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250507_FI_source-ap_PBC-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-22 17:20:29",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "三一重工今遞來港IPO申請 曾傳集資規模達15億美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大型A+H新股陸續有來，港交所(00388)資料顯示，三一重工(600031.SH)已遞交來港上市申請。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：三一重工官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250522_FI_source-web_Sany-3-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：三一重工官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250522_FI_source-web_Sany-3-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：三一重工官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">早前市場曾傳出，三一重工今次捲土重來發H股上市，集資規模約達15億美元。資料顯示，三一重工曾於2011年提出來港上市，但最後因市況而擱置有關計畫。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">三一重工的初步招股書顯示，今次發H股上市由中信里昂證券任整體協調人。該公司成立於1994年，是創新驅動的全球工程機械行業領軍企業。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：三一重工官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250522_FI_source-web_Sany-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：三一重工官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250522_FI_source-web_Sany-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：三一重工官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">根據弗若斯特沙利文的資料，按2020年至2024年核心工程機械的累計收入計算，三一重工是全球第3大及中國最大的工程機械企業。於往績記錄期間，該公司產品已銷往全球150餘個國家和地區，2024年海外市場收入佔總收入的62.3%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">三一重工母公司擁有人於2022年、2023年及2024年度應佔利潤，分別達43.01億元(人民幣．下同)、45.27億元及59.75億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14950067-%e4%b8%89%e4%b8%80%e9%87%8d%e5%b7%a5%e4%bb%8a%e9%81%9e%e4%be%86%e6%b8%afipo%e7%94%b3%e8%ab%8b-%e6%9b%be%e5%82%b3%e9%9b%86%e8%b3%87%e8%a6%8f%e6%a8%a1%e9%81%9415%e5%84%84%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250522_FI_source-web_Sany-3-2-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-22 17:15:31",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "全日收市｜港股收跌283點   科技股推低大市  比特幣概念逆升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股午後趺幅擴大，跌破上午低位，科技股成跌亦元兇，內需股也受壓，比特幣概念股逆市升。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數全日報23544，跌283點或1.19%，今早開市報23748點，跌79點或0.33%，最高見23778點，跌49點或0.21%，隨即向下，午後跌破上午低位，見23470，挫357點或1.5%，為全日低位。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250514_FI_source-web_01810-6.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250514_FI_source-web_0